headline: DET-IX Enhances Infrastructure with Arista 7060X5 Series Switches
summary: The Detroit Internet Exchange (DET-iX), Michigan's largest not-for-profit internet exchange, is proud to announce a major infrastructure upgrade featuring Arista Networks' state-of-the-art 7060X5 series switches. This investment marks a key step in DET-iX's ongoing mission to deliver high-speed, low-latency interconnection services to its expanding member community.
